OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 25 Mar to Fri 3 Apr
OL,6,FChangeable conditions for many parts
OL,7,Fof the UK at the start of this period,
OL,8,Fas areas of low pressure and their
OL,9,Fassociated frontal zones run close to
OL,10,For over the UK. These are likely to be
OL,11,Fmost active in the north and somewhat
OL,12,Fweaker further south, closer to a
OL,13,Fridge of high pressure extending
OL,14,Ftowards the UK from the west. There is
OL,15,Falso potential for a cooler period
OL,16,Fearly in this period, with some snow
OL,17,Fpossible in parts of the north. Into
OL,18,FApril, high pressure may become rather
OL,19,Fmore dominant once again with plenty
OL,20,Fof dry weather, but with some
OL,21,Fovernight fog and frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
